  "detailed_description": "Crash Forts 2 is a continuation of an exciting puzzle about physics and destruction. You have to destroy various structures again with the help of tools. In the game you will find a lot of new exciting and exciting levels of varying difficulty.<br />\r\nControl your hammer and pickaxe and destroy everything in your path! There are a lot of unique buildings waiting for you in the game, so destroy them all!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures of the game:<br />\r\n- Many levels<br />\r\n- Complete destruction of objects<br />\r\n- Physics<br />\r\n- Colorful graphics",
  "about_the_game": "Crash Forts 2 is a continuation of an exciting puzzle about physics and destruction. You have to destroy various structures again with the help of tools. In the game you will find a lot of new exciting and exciting levels of varying difficulty.<br />\r\nControl your hammer and pickaxe and destroy everything in your path! There are a lot of unique buildings waiting for you in the game, so destroy them all!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures of the game:<br />\r\n- Many levels<br />\r\n- Complete destruction of objects<br />\r\n- Physics<br />\r\n- Colorful graphics",
